She sat in the other conference room waiting for Iron Raptor.  She 
looked around the room.  She thought of her story and made sure she 
had it down.  she guessed that Iron Raptor wanted to make sure she 
hadn't been reprgramming into a Pred or something.  If she could fool 
one bot, she could fool the others as well, she thought, especially 
with the sob story she had. She smiled to herself and waited.
